  "description": "Add Language-Aware Navigation to About Page Button\n\nUpdate the \"dowiedz się więcej\" (learn more) button on the home page to direct users to the About page with proper language routing.\n\nRequirements:\n- Locate the \"dowiedz się więcej\" button component on the home page\n- Implement dynamic routing that preserves the current language context\n- Link should navigate to /{currentLanguage}/about (e.g., /pl/about, /en/about, /de/about)\n- Ensure the button works correctly for all supported language variants\n- Verify navigation maintains the language state throughout the user session\n- Test that the About page loads correctly when accessed via this button\n- Confirm the button styling and behavior remain unchanged",
